Description_lang: Your Healing Wave will now jump to additional nearby targets. Each jump reduces the effectiveness of the heal by 80%, and the spell will jump to up to two additional targets.

description_blz.en_US: Your Healing Wave will now jump to additional nearby targets. Each jump reduces the effectiveness of the heal by 80%, and the spell will jump to up to two additional targets.
description_blz.es_MX: Tu Ola de sanación saltará a otros objetivos cercanos. Cada salto reduce la eficacia de la sanación en un 80%. El hechizo saltará a un máximo de 2 objetivos extra.
description_blz.pt_BR: Sua Onda Curativa agora salta para alvos próximos. O feitiço saltará para até dois alvos, e cada salto reduz a eficácia da cura em 80%.
description_blz.de_DE: Euer Zauber 'Welle der Heilung' springt auf bis zu zwei zusätzliche Ziele über. Bei jedem Sprung reduziert sich die Effektivität der Heilung um 80%.
description_blz.en_GB: Your Healing Wave will now jump to additional nearby targets. Each jump reduces the effectiveness of the heal by 80%, and the spell will jump to up to two additional targets.
description_blz.es_ES: Tu Ola de sanación saltará a otros objetivos cercanos. Cada salto reduce la eficacia de la sanación en un 80%. El hechizo saltará a un máximo de 2 objetivos extra.
description_blz.fr_FR: Votre Vague de soins soigne aussi des cibles proches supplémentaires. Chaque nouveau soin perd 80% d'efficacité, et le sort soigne jusqu'à deux cibles supplémentaires.
description_blz.it_IT: Ondata di Cura ora colpisce bersagli aggiuntivi vicini. Ogni passaggio riduce l'efficacia della cura dell'80% e l'incantesimo colpisce fino a un massimo di 2 bersagli aggiuntivi.
description_blz.ru_RU: Исцеление множественных целей заклинанием "Волна исцеления", способным распространяться на соседние цели. Каждый из двух возможных переходов на соседнюю цель снижает эффект на 80%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 치유의 물결 사용 시 추가로 주위 아군을 연쇄적으로 회복시킵니다. 대상이 바뀔 때마다 치유 효과는 80%씩 감소합니다. 최대 2명의 추가 대상에게 효력을 미칩니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 你的治療波會治療一個額外的目標。治療波每次跳躍後的治療效果都會降低80%，並治療最多二個額外的目標。
description_blz.zh_CN: 你的治疗波会治疗一个额外的目标。治疗波每次跳跃后的治疗效果都会降低80%，治疗最多2个额外的目标。
